{"tid":1820353,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"牛扒 超高速 解凍法 之 風解","createTime":"2020-01-11T12:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T13:16:55.000Z","uid":105604,"like":17,"dislike":57,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"811017c58437bb4c1c43623fe20357ecea0b0b89","tid":1820353,"uid":105604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:56:58.000Z","msg":"大家有冇試過突然之間勁想食牛扒呢？<br />\n但啲牛扒仲係冰隔未解凍<br />\n而我就係冇牛扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n岩岩落佐去百街買急冰牛扒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4FCtLg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4FCtLg.jpg&h=38abe951&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁佢仲成舊冰咁，煎唔到<br />\n而我又想快食，但又要解凍<br />\n又想保持肉汁<br />\n靈機一觸<br />\n我發明佐新。超高速解凍法<br />\n。<br />\n風。解<br />\n。<br />\n<br />\n操作方法：<br />\n用將牛扒放係鐵盤上，<br />\n用風扇對住佢吹。完<br />\n<br />\n原理：<br />\n原不斷吹走佢散發係佢表面既冷空氣<br />\n達到持續而不斷地高超去冷達到高速解凍效果！<br />\n咁佢解解下會痴依個鐵盤<br />\n鐵盤會高速傳冷，吸走佢啲冷溫度<br />\n咁個風扇仲吹埋個鐵盤，類似cpu 散熱既反向操作！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1gZ7QZH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1gZ7QZH.png&h=f1b5d636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打佐鋪機，廿分鐘都冇，已經完成解凍！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hwmx18i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHwmx18i.png&h=b224c1d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3bf5eb265280066287d1f6ac479d49a7b029828","tid":1820353,"uid":31029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d9bfe016a72618a8e61b01f445a24cb26a45c4","tid":1820353,"uid":159583,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:58:40.000Z","msg":"立法會選舉後再返黎睇"},{"pid":"86e79c0de2345d3bfde8975f82bec549db8f5182","tid":1820353,"uid":90102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T12:59:35.000Z","msg":"下年再返黎睇